title: Isara antillensis
text: Isara antillensis is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a marine <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Mitridae">Mitridae</a>, the miters or miter snails.
